  <text>
    <body>
  <div type="scene" n="1">
    <head><app>
        <lem wit="#A #C #D #E">SCENE VI. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">SCENE X. </rdg>
      </app></head>
    <stage type='personnages'><app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E">JOCASTE, ANTIGONE, OLYMPE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">IOCASTE, ANTIGONE, OLYMPE. </rdg>
      </app></stage>
    <sp>
      <speaker>ANTIGONE.</speaker>
<l n="327">
LE perfide, à quel point son insolence monte&#160;! </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E">JOCASTE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">IOCASTE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="328">
Ses superbes discours tourneront à sa 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">honte, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">honte. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="329">
Bien-tost si nos desirs sont exaucez des Cieux, </l>

<l n="330">
La Paix nous vangera de 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">ces </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">cet </rdg>
      </app>
ambitieux. </l>

<l n="331">
Mais il faut se haster, chaque heure nous est chere, </l>

<l n="332">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Appellons&#160;au&#160;plus&#160;viste </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Appellons&#160;promptement </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Hemon </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Hémon </rdg>
      </app>
&amp; vostre Frere&#160;; </l>

<l n="333">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Ie </rdg>
      </app>
suis pour ce dessein preste à leur 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">accorder, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">accorder </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="334">
Toutes les 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">seûretez </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">seuretez </rdg>
      </app>
qu’ils pourront demander. </l>

<l n="335">
Et 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">toy, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">toi, </rdg>
      </app>
si mes 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">mal-heurs </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">malheurs </rdg>
      </app>
ont lassé ta justice, </l>

<l n="336">
Ciel, dispose à la Paix le cœur de Polinice, </l>

<l n="337">
Seconde mes soûpirs, donne force à mes pleurs, </l>

<l n="338">
Et comme il faut enfin, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">fais </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">fai </rdg>
      </app>
parler mes douleurs. </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker>ANTIGONE,</speaker>
      <stage type="stage-direction">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">demeurant un peu aprés sa Mere. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">demeurant vn peu aprés sa Mere. </rdg>
      </app>
      </stage>

<l n="339">
Et si tu prens pitié 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">d’une </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">d’vne </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">flamme </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">flâme </rdg>
      </app>
innocente, </l>

<l n="340">
O 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">Ciel&#160;! </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">ciel&#160;! </rdg>
      </app>
en ramenant 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Hemon </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Hémon </rdg>
      </app>
à son Amante, </l>

<l n="341">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Ramene&#160;le </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Ramene-le </rdg>
      </app>
fidelle, &amp; permets en ce 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">jour, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">iour, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="342">
Qu’en 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">retrouvant </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">retrouuant </rdg>
      </app>
l’Amant 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">ie </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">retrouve </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">retrouue </rdg>
      </app>
l’Amour. </l>

      <stage type="stage-direction">
Fin du premier Acte.       </stage>

</sp>
</div>
